startProxyServer

public boolean startProxyServer(String[] parameters)
starts a new proxy server.

Parameters:
parameters - array of String containing the parameters.
parameters[0] argument is always the method name,
parameters[1] argument is the Proxy listening port,
parameters[2] is the proxy name to append to the via header,
parameters[3] argument is the proxy timeout.
If only parameters[0] is submitted the parameters will be taken from the configuration xml document in XTTProperties.
If null is used as parameters it sends the allowed parameters list to the XTTProperties.printFail(java.lang.String) method and returns.

stopProxyServer

public boolean stopProxyServer(String[] parameters)
stops an instance of the proxy server..

Parameters:
parameters - array of String containing the parameters.
parameters[0] argument is always the method name,
parameters[1] is the proxy name.
If only parameters[0] is submitted the parameter will be taken from the configuration xml document in XTTProperties.
If null is used as parameters it sends the allowed parameters list to the XTTProperties.printFail(java.lang.String) method and returns.
